Um, Crow Lord, Prowl's on his way to the Ark.

::Striker/Ramulus/Shredder::

In the Cybertronian Fire, Striker walks up to Rhinox, looking at the maximal 
and the stuff on his back.

"You can pick a room and unpack. Most of the rooms are free."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus rolls out of the way of one of Shredder's shots, jumping at the 
attacking bot and swinging his gun. Shredder stumbles back as the gun slams 
across his face, leaving a mark, mech fluid quickly starting to pour out.

With an enraged yell, Shredder takes out his sword, jumping at Ramulus and 
swinging his sword.
